    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a source for parts. The engine currently struggles with consistent idling and there is a noticeable leak in the transmission system that will require immediate attention. Externally, the car has significant rust along the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling extensively across the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears in the seating, and several electronic components, including the radio and passenger-side window motor, are non-functional. It is currently not in reliable driving condition and will likely need to be towed.",
      "price": 4500.0,
